# Index Knowledge Base

Manually trigger indexing of configured knowledge base paths.

## Usage

```
/lsearch-index [path]
```

## Arguments

- `path` (optional): Specific path to index. If not provided, indexes all configured paths.

## Your task

1. Check the current lsearch configuration
2. Run lsearch index to build the knowledge base index
3. Report the results
